column10:
If you liked Chivalry, you'll love Mordhau! 
It is:
-Very intense;
-Skill-based like no other;
-full of weapons, items, interactables, horses;
-Full of eye candy;
-A Monty Python reference.

DO NOT PLAY/BUY (This game is one of if not the most Degen, Depressing games to ever exist)
Here's why 
You start the game and play (everyone who thinks they are better will let you know+more) {2019}

6 months later you are starting to get good (You begin to put in your hours in and lost your sanity to a community of racist Teens and Adults ) {2020}

1 Year and a half later 
Your at your Peak of skill and movement in Mordhau you win every lobby you enter and people hate you because of your level / skill / Armor {2021}

1 year later 
you fall off (you lost all Hope in people who play this game and only Gain Faster reflexes and A Darker mind if you play this game ) {2022}

ONCE again 1/10 for this game not good for you or your health DO NOT PLAY
